snippet.title: KINGDOM HEARTS HD 2.8 FINAL CHAPTER PROLOGUE & KINGDOM HEARTS III – Jump Festa 2015
snippet.description:
Are you prepared to face Xehanort? 
Is there a traitor among us?
What happened to Aqua in the Realm of Darkness?
Do you want to see a sneak peek at Kingdom Hearts III? 

Find out more information about all the magical content in Kingdom Hearts HD 2.8 Final Chapter Prologue, then prepare yourself for a sneak peek at Kingdom Hearts III and an all-new Attraction Flow attack!

The complete Kingdom Hearts saga to date is now in HD! Kingdom Hearts HD 2.8 Final Chapter Prologue contains the newly remastered Kingdom Hearts Dream Drop Distance, the cinematics from Kingdom Hearts Unchained χ [chi], and a special all new chapter taking place after the events of Kingdom Hearts Birth by Sleep. Coming 2016!
